mposed of the high- and\nlow-temperature polymorphs of ScF$_3$. However, some fine details in the\nexperimental results suggest that the probed powder sample may contain defects\nand/or residual traces of metastable polymorphs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Dec 2022 16:18:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Mar 2023 10:10:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-06"}
